{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset of interest is LegalBench, a benchmark built by a collaboration between lawyers and ML engineers to measure legal reasoning in LLMs (et al., 2023b).",
    "Llama-2-7b performs between 30-50% across all tasks, leaving room for improvement.",
    "When the LEARN algorithm was applied to the model for LegalBench, it showed marked improvement across all tasks.",
    "Table 3 shows the consistent improvement across tasks and a 40% boost to the average performance of the system compared to the base LLM.",
    "Training with LEARN is shown relative to traditional LoRA fine-tuning."
  ]
}